column2: "Oh, hello partner, what are you doing here?"
"You chased after me here? Sorry, I was going after someone's shadow."
"<%me>, finally, I managed to reach you."
"After not coming, I was wondering what happened to you."
"Sorry Fourier, partner saw me and caught up to me."
"Probably not the best time to ask for a favor, but would you mind if I borrowed <%me> today?"
"Does it have to do with why you've been depressed lately?"
"I'm not sure, maybe. We'll have to wait and see."
"Understood. You don't need to worry about me, this planet is like my yard now."
"Sorry for deciding that on my own, partner."
"I could have asked to meet up, but I don't think there's time for that."
"That Dark Falz might have come here before."
"That Falz that we met right after the ARKS Battle Tournament..."
"What? We didn't attend that together. But when I saw it, weren't you...?"
"Anyway, I need to focus on what's in front of me right now. I'm counting on you, partner."
"3章 霞んだ記憶、欠けた記録"
